<div id="page_head"><span style="width: 100%;"><a name="skip_menu"></a></span>
  <h1>Library of Congress Pavilion</h1>
</div>
<!-- end id:page_head -->
<div class="box_img"><img src="http://www.loc.gov/bookfest/images/banner_lcpavilion.jpg" width="694" height="140" alt="" /></div>
<p>The Library of Congress Pavilion offers an in-depth look at the many ways the Library brings its extraordinary resources to Congress and the American people everywhere. A variety of special exhibits will be on view, and you can hear from representatives of the various Library divisions on the work they do to collect, share and preserve the creative and intellectual heritage of the nation at the world’s largest library. </p>

<ul class="tabnav">
   <li class="first"><a href="#tab1">Saturday, Sept. 21</a></li>
   <li><a href="#tab2">Sunday, Sept. 22</a></li>
</ul>
<!-- end class:tabnav -->
